In this video, i will show you how to view source code or HTML code of any website on Android Mobile in google chrome or any browser. 1. Open the Google Chrome browser on your Android phone or tablet. 2. Open the web page whose source code you'd like to view. 3. Tap once in the address bar and move the cursor to the front of the URL. 4. Type view-source: and tap Enter or Go.
